Package applications.mnist

Class Mnist

  • java.lang.Object
    • applications.Application
      • applications.mnist.Mnist
  • public class Mnist
extends Application
    Implementation of Application, contains basic methods needed to train a NeuralNetwork on the Mnist dataset of handwritten digits.
    Author:
    OdinhengeT
    See Also:
    AppliedNetwork, Application, NeuralNetwork, MnistFileReader, MnistDataVisualizer

    • Method Summary

      All Methods Instance Methods Concrete Methods 
      Modifier and Type Method Description
      double[][][] getEvaluationDataD()
      Returns the collection of Evaluation images and labels (downloaded from the Mnist website) as a double[][][], first index: 0 for images 1 for labels; second index corresponds to which set of evaluationData; the images and labels have been vectorized, so the thrid index corresponds to a specific entry of the labe/image.
      float[][][] getEvaluationDataF()
      Returns the collection of Evaluation images and labels (downloaded from the Mnist website) as a float[][][], first index: 0 for images 1 for labels; second index corresponds to which set of evaluationData; the images and labels have been vectorized, so the thrid index corresponds to a specific entry of the labe/image.
      double[][][] getTrainingDataD​(int nbrSets)
      Returns a collection of nbrSets sets of trainig images and labels (downloaded from the Mnist website) as a double[][][], first index: 0 for images 1 for labels; second index corresponds to which set of trainingData; the images and labels have been vectorized, so the thrid index corresponds to a specific entry of the labe/image.
      float[][][] getTrainingDataF​(int nbrSets)
      Returns a collection of nbrSets sets of trainig images and labels (downloaded from the Mnist website) as a double[][][], first index: 0 for images 1 for labels; second index corresponds to which set of trainingData; the images and labels have been vectorized, so the thrid index corresponds to a specific entry of the labe/image.
      void loadD()
      Loads the data from the files downloaded from the Mnist website into the double[][] above, and changes isDataLoaded to true.
      void loadF()
      Loads the data from the files downloaded from the Mnist website into the float[][] above, and changes isDataLoaded to true.
      java.lang.String runDiagnosticD​(NeuralNetwork network)
      Evaluates a NeuralNetwork using the Evaluation data and returns a String containing the results of the diagnostic.
